file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: '1.0'
  title: 'FizzBuzz'
  description: 'Prints FizzBuzz based on input.'
# Added by API Auto Mocking Plugin
servers:
  - description: SwaggerHub API Auto Mocking
    url: https://virtserver.swaggerhub.com/JonathanSorem/FizzBuzz/1.0

# Basic authentication
components:
  securitySchemes:
    BasicAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: basic
security:
  - BasicAuth: []

paths:
  /map:
    get: 
      description: Prints FizzBuzz
      parameters:
        - name: latitude
          in: query
          description: Input
          schema:
            type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successfully printed FizzBuzz
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: List
                items:
                  type: integer
                  required:
                    - input
                  properties:
                    fizzbuzz:
                      type: integer
        '400':
          description: Invalid request
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:   
                  message:
                    type: string
